title: Spain and Switzerland book Euro 2016 places (PFA - Professional Footballers' Association)
text: ( Source : PFA - Professional Footballers' Association ) Spain and Switzerland stamped their tickets for France next summer in their penultimate games of European Championship qualifying. Spain, the 2012 champions, began the night five points
